  "data": [
    [
      [
        "[Fabian]. I think I really got along with him, so… yeah."
      ],
      [
        "I think [he]’s the one that I want to date."
      ],
      [
        "Say no more! I’ll help you arrange everything so… get ready for your date!"
      ],
      [
        "I can’t believe it, this is really happening!"
      ],
      [
        "My first date with someone I actually like."
      ],
      [
        "This day was just getting better and better."
      ],
      [
        "For now, it was time to change into something nicer, and go for a proper date with [Fabian]."
      ],
      [
        "I quickly run back to my house and put on one of my nicest outfits."
      ],
      [
        "I know Helpie is taking care of the arrangements of the date,"
      ],
      [
        "so I really just have to focus on looking my best."
      ],
      [
        "I wait for a little while until Helpie calls me. "
      ],
      [
        "Everything is set up [tn]."
      ],
      [
        "[Fabian] will be waiting for you at the park."
      ],
      [
        "I heard [he]’s got a surprise for youuu."
      ],
      [
        "My heart thumped rapidly as I heard the last part."
      ],
      [
        "And with that, I leave towards the park."
      ],
      [
        ""
      ],
      [
        "The sun shines as I arrive there and begin looking for [Fabián]."
      ],
      [
        "The park is filled with beautiful and tall trees, with a lot of places to go sit and relax."
      ],
      [
        "Maybe it would have been nice to meet up in a specific place, but oh well."
      ],
      [
        "I look around, trying to figure out where my date could be."
      ],
      [
        "When suddenly, I feel two hands grab me by the shoulders."
      ],
      [
        "Boo!"
      ],
      [
        "AAAAAH!!!!"
      ],
      [
        "I turn around and just find [Fabian]’s cheeky grin, smiling at me."
      ],
      [
        "hahaha! Look at your face!"
      ],
      [
        "I wish I had a camera on me right now."
      ],
      [
        "I roll my eyes, but still find myself chuckling at the joke. "
      ],
      [
        "Welp, I’m glad you could make it."
      ],
      [
        "I don’t know if Helpie told you, but I’ve got something prepared for you."
      ],
      [
        "So… let’s get walking."
      ],
      [
        "As we walk, we enjoy a comfortable silence."
      ],
      [
        "Still, I really want to get to know [Fabian], and this was the perfect opportunity to do so. "
      ],
      [
        "So, [Fabian]…"
      ]
